plyTime":"2016-12-22T10:33:50.000Z","msg":"林鄭會出一大輪捐錢扶貧節目，叫香港人捐錢，再唔捐就自割港庫出去"},{"pid":"fd4a70410692bc88e1ce787f537b579c0f4fc052","tid":49731,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"攞著午餐肉返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}